"{\"uid\": \"nbcsports.com-olympics-news-usa-olympic-team-mountain-bike-cycling-paris-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"A young, decorated group of mountain bikers have a chance to win the U.S.' first Olympic medals in the discipline in 12 years and its first gold medal ever.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 156, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The U.S. qualified the maximum two women's and two men's quota spots for the Paris Olympics through international results over the last two years.\", \"from\": 158, \"to\": 304, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The full team will be named later this month, but three Americans already met objective criteria to fill Olympic spots.\", \"from\": 306, \"to\": 425, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Haley Batten was ninth in her Olympic debut in Tokyo, then took bronze at the 2022 World Championships.\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 530, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 427, \"end\": 439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haley_Batten\", \"score\": 0.999997827362081, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Haley Batten\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haley_Batten\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haley_Batten\"}, {\"begin\": 474, \"end\": 479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9949728578972314, \"rank\": 0.004966695489428016, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TEAM USA:List of athletes qualified for Paris Olympics  The 25-year-old from Utah placed in the top three in each of the three World Cups held so far in 2024, including her first career victory on that level.\", \"from\": 532, \"to\": 740, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 572, \"end\": 586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wik